                     rf-mmr-num-mag       not  = w-ssm-mtv-num-mag
                     go to ssm-mtv-stp-600.
           if        rf-mmr-dat-reg       >    w-ssm-mtv-dat-max
                     go to ssm-mtv-stp-600.
       ssm-mtv-stp-400.
