           if        w-ssm-mtv-snx-srf    not  = 01
                     go to ssm-mtv-stp-440.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Accumulo su totali                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   ssm-mtv-stp-act-000  thru ssm-mtv-stp-act-999    .
       ssm-mtv-stp-440.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Editing preliminare dei valori da stampare re-  *
      *              * lativi al movimento                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   ssm-mtv-edt-mov-000  thru ssm-mtv-edt-mov-999    .
       ssm-mtv-stp-460.
