           if        w-ssm-mtv-flg-stp    not  = spaces
                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-prn-flg-int
                     go to ssm-mtv-stp-999.
       ssm-mtv-stp-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa riepilogo finale                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
