      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      0100                 to   d-sld-mag-tip-sld      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data saldo : data minima movimenti di-  *
      *                      *              minuita di un giorno       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-mtv-dat-mmu    to   d-sld-mag-dat-sld      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Una o tutte le dipendenze               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "U"                  to   d-sld-mag-uot-dpz      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice dipendenza                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-mtv-cod-dpz    to   d-sld-mag-cod-dpz      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
