      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-mtv-tip-mag    to   d-sld-mag-tip-mag      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice di magazzino                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-mtv-num-mag    to   d-sld-mag-num-mag      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
