      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa scheda elemento in esame, calcolo finale totali    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       ssm-mtv-stp-cft-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totali 'Magazzino fisico'                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * 'Fine periodo'                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-mtv-tpc-mfi    to   w-ssm-mtv-tpc-mff      .
           add       w-ssm-mtv-tpc-mfc    to   w-ssm-mtv-tpc-mff      .
           subtract  w-ssm-mtv-tpc-mfs    from w-ssm-mtv-tpc-mff      .
       ssm-mtv-stp-cft-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totali 'Proprieta' inizio periodo'              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * 'Magazzino fisico'                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-mtv-tpc-mfi    to   w-ssm-mtv-tpc-pim      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * 'Di proprieta''                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-ssm-mtv-tpc-pim    to   w-ssm-mtv-tpc-pip      .
           add       w-ssm-mtv-tpc-pin    to   w-ssm-mtv-tpc-pip      .
           subtract  w-ssm-mtv-tpc-pit    from w-ssm-mtv-tpc-pip      .
       ssm-mtv-stp-cft-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totali 'Proprieta' fine periodo'                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * 'Magazzino fisico'                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
